like this one.

58
00:06:19.167 --> 00:06:20.874
Did you ever hear
so much talk about nothin'?

59
00:06:20.958 --> 00:06:22.832
Well, I guess they're entitled.

60
00:06:22.917 --> 00:06:25.375
Yeah. They're entitled.
It's the system, but...

61
