68
00:06:44.292 --> 00:06:46.292
I, uh... Well, I guess so.

69
00:06:51.042 --> 00:06:52.500
Uh, you're in my seat.

70
00:06:52.583 --> 00:06:54.583
- Oh. Excuse me.
- That's all right.

71
00:06:57.125 --> 00:06:59.125
Hey, that's not a bad view, huh?

72
00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:04.957
