627
00:33:25.417 --> 00:33:27.436
It doesn't matter. He's
very excitable. Sit down.

628
00:33:27.460 --> 00:33:28.874
Excitable? You
bet I'm excitable!

629
00:33:28.958 --> 00:33:31.791
